dc_description_s: This polygon data layer represents hydrography for Fond du Lac County, Wisconsin in 2017. It is a feature class within the geodatabase Fond_du_Lac_Hydro_2017.gdb.[Open water features were generated from the digital orthophotography obtained in 2000. All work was done by Ayers Associates.]
